                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>omino</ex></expan> Marti <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Tittulli<lb break="no" n="4"/>us Avitin<lb break="no" n="5"/>us <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Aus einem Hortfund; Fundjahr: 1961-1973. Votivblech; die Inschrift befindet sich in dem Aedicula-Feld über dem Schaft. Schreibtechnik: eingeritzt. Buchstaben zur Kursive neigend. (B): AE 1999: Z. 3/4: Titulli/us.</p>
            </div>
